title: Superman - The Complete Geoff Johns Era
description:
Included in this torrent is the complete Geoff Johns run on Action Comics, a small stint on Superman and the mini-series Secret Origin which lasted from 2006-2008 and 2009-2010(Secret Origin). Everything has been placed in correct reading order including the two annuals that took place during the Last Son arc. Due to the nature of his run and a brief hiatus during Last Son, I will be compiling a torrent that covers the entire Chris Kent Saga, as to better understand the complete story line that was undertaken by other writers as well. 

-Secret Origin 
-Up, Up and Away
-Last Son
-Escape from Bizarro World
-Superman and the Legion of Super-Heroes
-Brainiac
